  "description": "Guru Bin signature #15. A 30-second Jungian journey in one held chord. Begins in the Shadow archetype — dark, detuned, subharmonic. First peak transitions to Anima. The dip allows acausal clusters to bloom unpredictably (ResSens=0.7). Second peak arrives at Hero — full synchrony, bright, powerful. A complete archetypal summoning.",
